overview: Tells the story of a quarrel between two women due to a misunderstanding. A woman who trades cakes at a stall helps another woman by taking her as an assistant and eventually helping her start a business with her. Misunderstandings began to occur when the cake that was introduced began to get the attention of many and the women he helped were friends with the man who had been his idol.
title: Kuba Guling Karipap Pusing
